## Africana Studies Relation

**Africana Studies Relation:**  
Cornel West’s contributions provide a critical perspective on Black intellectual history, social movements, and the intersections of race and class. His work serves as a foundational element in modern Africana Studies, offering insights into ongoing struggles for justice and equality.

